🔹 Steps to Add Trigger

Open your Apps Script project.

Click on Triggers (left sidebar → clock icon).

Click “+ Add Trigger”.

Configure as follows:

Choose function to run → generateQRCodes

Deployment → Head

Event source → Time-driven

Type of time based trigger → Minute timer

Select minute interval → Every 1 minute (or 5 minutes if you prefer)

Save the trigger.
